<DL>
 <DT>Syntax:
 <DD>
  <OL><LI><CODE>Let</CODE> <VAR>var</VAR> <CODE>:=</CODE> <VAR>term</VAR>
      <LI><CODE>Let</CODE> <VAR>var</VAR> <CODE>:=</CODE> <VAR>term</VAR>
                                          <CODE>:</CODE> <VAR>term2</VAR>
  </OL> 
 <DT>Effect:
 <DD>Adds a definition to the local context.
</DL>